    <PrimAttribute name="camsTimeStamp" id="344396e0-2fc5-442f-bfe8-5ed0945fe53d">
        <embedded/>
        <type name="TimeStamp"/>
        <access>readonly</access>
        <text>Added for PAR #24065.  Will be set by an update to a transaction which occurs after it has been created.

The conditional collection on CM_Terminal (allTITransactionsByEDIDateTime) will then have this transaction
added to it, so that it can be picked up by CAMS processing if required.</text>
    </PrimAttribute>
