    <PrimAttribute name="superseded" id="ca9ae933-b5a8-47c1-8cf9-4fe504259076">
        <embedded/>
        <virtual/>
        <type name="Boolean"/>
        <access>readonly</access>
        <text>&lt;Documentation&gt;
&lt;Description&gt;
A flag to indicate that this trasaction has been edited by a user (refer amended above) and hence has been superceded by.  
When a user edits a transaction the system takes a copy of the old transaction (setting this flag to true) for auditing purposes.
&lt;/Description&gt;
&lt;/Documentation&gt;</text>
    </PrimAttribute>
